{"badges":["TM31","TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 190°C. Line a baking tray (30 x 40 cm) with baking paper and set aside.","Hollow out the centre of each mushroom cap (reserving stems) to create space for filling and place, hollow-side up, onto baking tray.","Place almonds into mixing bowl and mill <b>10 sec\/speed 8<b>. Transfer into a bowl and set aside.","Place Parmesan into mixing bowl and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 9<b>. Transfer into a separate bowl and set aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl.","Place butter and oil into mixing bowl and heat <b>1 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Transfer 2 tablespoons of the melted butter mixture into a small bowl and set aside.","Add eschalots, garlic, egg, parsley, nutmeg, salt, pepper and mushroom stems to mixing bowl and cook <b>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>.","Add reserved grated Parmesan and mix <b>10 sec\/speed 6<b>.","Brush each mushroom entirely with the reserved melted butter mixture and carefully spoon 1½ teaspoons of the mushroom mixture into each mushroom cap and sprinkle with reserved almonds. Place onto prepared tray and bake for 20 minutes (190°C - see Tip), until golden on top. Serve while warm."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["16 fresh cup mushrooms, brushed clean (stems removed and reserved)","20 g blanched almonds","40 g Parmesan cheese","40 g butter","30 g olive oil","60 g eschalots, cut into quarters","1 garlic clove","1 egg","½ bunch fresh flat-leaf parsley, leaves only","1 pinch ground nutmeg","½ tsp salt, to taste","1 - 2 pinches ground black pepper"]}],"id":"r260525","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-xVh-MoehPLc\/XZMvcRivKwI\/AAAAAAAAaR4\/A0_L40wcJaw7SRQ6w7EO2tRB9jx4dRJ2ACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_gAiD1TIQhJI_xnw_.png","title":"Mushroom-stuffed mushrooms","publishedAt":"2018-02-18T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{},"usefulItems":"bowl, baking tray (30 x 40 cm), baking paper, pastry brush, small bowl, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Cooking time may vary depending on the size of your mushrooms. We recommend using medium to large mushrooms for this recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","50m","4 portions"]}